text: Deniz Türüç (born 29 January 1993 in Enschede, Netherlands) is a Dutch-born professional footballer. He plays as a midfielder. He is currently on loan at İstanbul Başakşehir from Fenerbahçe. He also plays for the Turkey national team. He scored his first goal for Turkey against Moldova in their 4-0 win on 10 September 2019.
